## Common Issues

| Symptom | Likely cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `auth is not a function` in middleware | Used `auth()` wrapper (Auth.js pattern) | Switch to cookie check: `request.cookies.get("better-auth.session_token")` (pitfall #43) |
| Sessions silently rejected | `BETTER_AUTH_URL` mismatch (trailing slash, port, scheme) | Make it exactly match the served URL (pitfall — Cookie domain) |
| `next build` fails on `/reset-password` | `useSearchParams()` without `<Suspense>` | Keep the `<Suspense>` wrapper — it's required in Next.js 14+ App Router (pitfall #47) |
| `forgetPassword is not a function` | Used old API name | Use `authClient.requestPasswordReset()` (pitfall #38) |
| `Unrecognized key 'serverExternalPackages'` | Wrong Next.js version syntax | Next.js 14: `experimental: { serverComponentsExternalPackages: [...] }`; Next.js 15+: `serverExternalPackages: [...]` (pitfall #42) |
<!-- IF email=resend -->
| Resend emails never arrive | Free-tier restriction | Verify your domain at [resend.com/domains](https://resend.com/domains), or send only to your account email |
| `Missing API key` during build | `new Resend()` at module scope | Use lazy-init pattern from `assets/config/email.ts` (pitfall #50) |
<!-- /IF -->

Full pitfall reference (60 production issues):
→ [`references/09-common-pitfalls.md`](https://github.com/MangalaHQ/shipwithai-plugins/blob/main/plugins/auth/skills/auth-setup/references/09-common-pitfalls.md)

