## Production Checklist

- [ ] Set `BETTER_AUTH_SECRET`, `BETTER_AUTH_URL`, `DATABASE_URL` in your hosting provider
- [ ] `BETTER_AUTH_URL` matches the deployed URL exactly (no trailing slash)
<!-- IF oauth=google -->
- [ ] Production redirect URI added in Google Cloud Console: `https://yourapp.com/api/auth/callback/google`
- [ ] OAuth consent screen submitted for verification (or set to **In production**)
<!-- /IF -->
<!-- IF email=resend -->
- [ ] Verified domain at Resend → switched `EMAIL_FROM` to `auth@yourdomain.com`
<!-- /IF -->
- [ ] `rateLimit` enabled in `auth.ts` (defaults: 10 req / 60s — tune for your app)
- [ ] Security headers from `next.config.ts` reviewed
- [ ] DB migrations run in production (`npx drizzle-kit push` or your CI pipeline)
- [ ] Run `npx ts-node scripts/verify-auth-setup.ts` and confirm all checks pass

